Squalus acanthias
not Linnaeus: 
Zhu 1960
: 107-109 (description; Northwest Pacific Ocean); 
Zhu and Meng 2001
: 310-313 (description; Northwest Pacific Ocean); 
Nakabo 2002
: 155 (listed; Japan); 
